/#
   Defines stock loan information where this is required per underlyer. You must not duplicate infromation within dividend conditions at transaction level
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.UnderlyerLoanRate {
  # If true, then loss of stock borrow is applicable.
  lossOfStockBorrow : boolean?

  # Specifies the maximum stock loan rate for Loss of Stock Borrow.
  maximumStockLoanRate : decimal?

  # If true, then increased cost of stock borrow is applicable.
  increasedCostOfStockBorrow : boolean?

  # Specifies the initial stock loan rate for Increased Cost of Stock Borrow.
  initialStockLoanRate : decimal?

}

lossOfStockBorrow.Doc: If true, then loss of stock borrow is applicable.
lossOfStockBorrow.Name: lossOfStockBorrow

maximumStockLoanRate.Doc: Specifies the maximum stock loan rate for Loss of Stock Borrow.
maximumStockLoanRate.Name: maximumStockLoanRate

increasedCostOfStockBorrow.Doc: If true, then increased cost of stock borrow is applicable.
increasedCostOfStockBorrow.Name: increasedCostOfStockBorrow

initialStockLoanRate.Doc: Specifies the initial stock loan rate for Increased Cost of Stock Borrow.
initialStockLoanRate.Name: initialStockLoanRate
